overview: Eddie Kingston and Larry Sweeney end their feud with a “Tex‑Arkana Yellow Bellied Strap” match! In an unforgettable moment, Hallowicked, Delirious, Deliriouscito, and Hallowickedcito take on UltraMantis Black, Hydra, Crossbones, and the returning Blind Rage. Max Boyer defends his Young Lions Cup, and The Colony unites for trios action!
title: Chikara: Talent Borrows; Genius Steals
